    "##\n",
    "\n",
    "E. La probabilidad de anotar entre 7 y 11 canastas, $P(7 \\leq X \\leq 11)$.\n",
    "\n",
    "Para este caso, debemos de ver \n",
    "\n",
    "::: {style=\"font-size: 85%;\"}\n",
    "$$P(7 \\leq X \\leq 11) = P(X \\leq 11) - P(X < 7) = P(X \\leq 11) - P(X \\leq 6).$$\n",
    ":::\n",
    "\n",
    "</br>\n",
    "\n",
    "En Python, esto se logra como sigue:"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 9,
   "id": "a2df2d82",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
